com.wm.xmldata

Class XmlDataAttributeTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wm.xmldata.XmlDataTag
      • com.wm.xmldata.XmlDataAttributeTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class XmlDataAttributeTag
extends XmlDataTag
    The XmlDataAttributeTag class constructs an XmlData attribute-tag from its constituent parts. It may also be used to parse an attribute-tag into its component parts. There is a methods that return the full-name for use in an XmlData infoset, but there is no path-name for an attribute. In addition, attribute are unique and unordered within an element, and are position-independent, and therefore, do not have a particle-id.

    It's format is: 

     
     ncName#namespace
